name: CENTCOM HQ
desc: The Draconis Alliance CENTCOM is the uncompromising answer to the question of Fafnir’s security. Conceived in the earliest days of the alliance, this massive subterranean complex serves as the strategic brain and backbone of the system’s spaceborne defences. From its fortified command decks, fleet officers direct orbital pickets, coordinate deep-space patrols, and stand ready to unleash Kori’s planetary batteries—railguns and missile silos buried so deep that only the most determined siege could hope to silence them.
